is closely following the situation in view of the enormous impact
of the Palestinian issue on the Middle East peace process at
present and also in the future.
</P>
<P>
Egypt hopes the three-way summit will succeed in bridging the
gaps between the Palestinians and Israelis, end up by realizing the
much touted and aspired "peace of the brave" and reach a just
solution to the Palestinian question which is at the core of the
Arab-Israeli conflict over the past half century, Moussa said.
