<HEADLINE> Asia's First Human Resource Website Launched </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, July 6 (Xinhua) -- Rewardasia, the first website
dedicated to human resource (HR) management in Asia, was
officially launched Thursday simultaneously in Hong Kong and
Singapore.
</P>
<P>
Created for the global HR community, Rewardasia is aimed at
providing corporate managers and HR practitioners with the tool
they need to manage human resource in Asia within a global
environment.
</P>
<P>
Unlike other HR site that contains one aspect of HR information,
Rewardasia offers free information, news, links, events agenda and
research papers with more than 25 topics and covering more than 25
countries and regions in Asia.
</P>
<P>
Visitors can read daily-updated news from more than 400
business media sources and find linkages to HR-related
institutions, government bodies and private organizations in
whichever Asian countries and regions selected. 
</P>
</TEXT>
