<HEADLINE> Military Leaders Watch Air Force Display </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 6 (Xinhua) -- China's top military leaders Zhang
Wannian and Chi Haotian watched an aerobatics display and drills
put on by the air force of the People's Liberation Army here today.
</P>
<P>
