Communist Party Central Committee, noted that the show displayed
the fruits of the air forces' training, with the emphasis on
science and technology.
</P>
<P>
The experience and methods of the air force should be promoted
throughout military, said Zhang, also vice-chairman of the Central
Military Commission.
</P>
<P>
Zhang also called on the Chinese military to put more emphasis
on learning science and new technology, and master new equipment.
