<HEADLINE> Bank Promises Credit to Wuhan's "Optical Valley" </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WUHAN, July 6 (Xinhua) -- The Bank of China's Hubei branch
signed an agreement today with the municipal government of this
capital of Hubei Province, promising huge amounts of credit for
the building of an "Optical Valley" in the city.
</P>
<P>
