largest optical and electronics information base, which is
expected to have a yearly output worth 100 billion yuan in five
years.
</P>
<P>
Tu Xiangru, president of the bank's Hubei branch, said that the
Bank of China has a keen interest in participating in the
construction of "Optical Valley," and is ready to provide a full
range of financial services to businesses involved in the project.
