<HEADLINE> FIFA Executive Committee Members </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GENEVA, July 6 (Xinhua) -- Following are the 24 members of the
FIFA executive committee who will vote to decide which country
hosts the 2006 World Cup
finals:
</P>
