<HEADLINE> China Opens Air Link With New Zealand </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Auckland, July 6 (Xinhua) -- Direct air service between the
People's Republic of China and New Zealand commenced as a Boing747-
400 of Air China arrived at Auckland International Airport
Thursday.
</P>
