</P>
<P>
The total volume contracted to 344.55 million units valued at
513.90 million Singapore dollars (296.25 million U.S. dollars).
Losers outstripped gainers by 231 to 90 with 228 counters
unchanged.
</P>
<P>
----
</P>
<P>
WELLINGTON -- The New Zealand sharemarket closed lower Thursday.
</P>
<P>
The NZSE40 Index ended 8 points lower at 2,040 with a heavy
turnover of 242.9 million NZ dollars (111.8 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
</TEXT>
