<P>
BEIJING, July 6 (Xinhua)-- Chinese Foreign Ministry spokesman
Sun Yuxi said that China welcomes the summit meeting by Palestine,
Israel, and the United States, to be held next week in the U.S.
</P>
<P>
He made the remark here today at a regular press conference in
response to a question requesting comments on this issue.
</P>
<P>
Sun said that China supports any effort that is conducive to
pushing forward the Mideast peace talks, adding that China
sincerely hopes the summit meeting will end up with positive
results, so as to bring about substantial progress in the peace
talks. 
</P>
