<HEADLINE> Young, Middle-aged Technicians Play Big Role in Navy Modernization </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 6 (Xinhua) -- Thousands of young and middle-aged
technical staff have become the backbone in modernizing the Navy
of the Chinese People's Liberation Army (PLA).
</P>
<P>
Over the past five years, technical personnel of the PLA Navy,
many of whom hold master's degrees or Ph.D.s, have won over 1,000
national prizes for inventions and technical progress in the
fields of war-preparation, training, armament and logistics.
</P>
