pharmacognostical evaluation of medicinal plants.
</P>
<P>
Moreover, workshops on registration and licensing of
traditional medicine, conservation and cultivation of herbal and
medicinal plants, and extraction of essential oil and marketing of
medicinal plants will also be held.
</P>
