<HEADLINE> Dalian to Become IT Hub </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 6 (Xinhua) -- The key port city of Dalian in
Northeast China will speed up the development of information
technology and electrical communication to enhance incoming and
existing businesses.
</P>
<P>
