ANKARA -- Turkish Appeals Court Wednesday upheld a one-year
imprisonment sentence imposed on Necmettin Erbakan, former prime
minister and leader of the outlawed Islamic Welfare Party, Anatolia
News Agency reported.
</P>
<P>
