<P>
JERUSALEM -- Israeli Interior Minister Natan Sharansky Wednesday
announced the withdrawal of his party, Yisrael Ba'aliya, from the
coalition government of Prime Minister Ehud Barak.
</P>
<P>
Sharansky made the statement just after U.S. President Bill
Clinton announced at the White House earlier in the day that a
