<HEADLINE> Strong Earthquake Hits Nicaragua </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The epicenter was in the Lake of Apoyo, in the Granada
department, some 50 kilometers southeast from the capital city of
Managua, with depth of only one kilometer, said the source.
</P>
<P>
People of the capital went out from their houses or apartments
